---
description: Advanced interaction system including cursor, hover, and micro-interactions
globs: ["components/**/*", "app/**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

## CURSOR SYSTEM

- Replace default cursor when appropriate
- Use custom cursor with:
  - Scale changes
  - Text hints (e.g., "View", "Open")
- Cursor should react to interactive elements

## MAGNETIC ELEMENTS

- Buttons and links should have magnetic pull
- Movement must be subtle and responsive

## HOVER SYSTEM

- Every interactive element must respond to hover
- Use:
  - Scale
  - Translate
  - Opacity
- Avoid default browser behavior

## CLICK FEEDBACK

- Add subtle press animation
- Provide tactile feel

## TRANSITIONS

- No abrupt changes
- Everything transitions smoothly

## NAVIGATION

- Avoid basic navbars
- Consider:
  - Overlay menu
  - Animated transitions
  - Minimal UI

## MICRO-INTERACTIONS

- Small details matter:
  - Link underline animations
  - Button movement
  - Section transitions

## RULE

The site should feel alive and responsive to the user.
